data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED! This property consist of 3 bedrooms 2.5 bathrooms 2,403 living space built in 2020. The downstairs consist of a large living room, family room, breakfast area, half bathroom, kitchen, and a 2-car garage with plenty of space to store all your toys. The second floor consist of a sitting area, 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a laundry room. The community has a clubhouse, swimming pool, state of the art fitness center & a social room. There are Charter schools, shops, restaurants & entertainment nearby and this property is located near the Florida Turnpike which provides access to the Florida Keys and the Miami area!
